      • equals

        public boolean equals​(Object obj)
        Indicates whether some other object is "equal to" this one.

        The result is true if and only if the argument is not null and is a BooleanValue object that represents the same value as this object.

        Overrides:

        public Calendar getDate()
                 throws ValueFormatException,
                        IllegalStateException,
                        RepositoryException
        Returns a Calendar representation of this value.

        The object returned is a copy of the stored value, so changes to it are not reflected in internal storage.
